re for </div><div class="t m68c x10 h12 y4ca ff3 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that wonderful event. What a grand privilege God gives His </div><div class="t m322 x10 h12 y4cb ff3 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">children, not only to know about these climactic events but to </div><div class="t m754 x7d h12 y8ae ff3 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">share them with all people! </div><div class="t m8f4 x7d h12 y1ea ff3 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">96 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
